                <text id="805:10103" name="The online 300-hour YTT improves a trainer&#39;s comprehension of core yoga principles and teachings covered in the RYT200 TTC worldwide yoga certification programme. Our yoga teacher training module equips students with more sophisticated yoga techniques in line with current trends, allowing them to instruct their students with confidence in the future." x="0" y="0" width="1273" height="81" />
              </frame>
              <text id="805:10104" name="After completing this advanced course, you will be certified as a RYT300 international yoga trainer and will be able to launch a successful career." x="0" y="93" width="1274" height="27" />
              <text id="805:10105" name="This 300 Hour TTC offered by Bodhi School of Yoga is accredited and recognised by Yoga Alliance. On a journey of self-discovery and profound transformation, our 300-Hour Yoga Teacher Training Course is carefully curated — designed to elevate both your personal practice and teaching skills." x="0" y="132" width="1274" height="54" />
